{"tid":2134704,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人氣偶像團體SKE48運營公司董事因猥褻少女被逮捕","createTime":"2020-08-01T02:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T05:11:42.000Z","uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c720d233f75bf161ec98c52d8ba39901f8727bd","tid":2134704,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"日本神奈川警方在本日（28日）逮捕了人氣偶像團體SKE48的運營公司的董事海老根一也（58歲）。該犯罪嫌疑人涉嫌違法兒童色情禁止法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.dmzj.com/resource/news/2020/07/28/1595926989759802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.dmzj.com%2Fresource%2Fnews%2F2020%2F07%2F28%2F1595926989759802.jpg&h=f0a4d141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據警方透露，海老根一也在去年11月23日，在東京都町田市內的停車場，以約定給現金的方式，與無職少女（當時15歲）和高中2年級女生（當時17歲）二人，進行了猥褻行為。不過海老根一也否認自己進行過猥褻，稱：&ldquo;只是讓她們上了車&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\nSKE48誕生於2008年，以名古屋市為中心展開活動，目前有成員70餘人。"},{"pid":"80e154f6c221bc6f6292477b7a46e3b3f5097f14","tid":2134704,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"風紀Wow咗好耐-.-"},{"pid":"ba58d18bed0258fddb780e2c0b0c3083dc842b2d","tid":2134704,"uid":205522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"48個都唔夠玩"},{"pid":"72cb97abb3e9db447817cc4ce218b0564a599347","tid":2134704,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>/u/動物成份</blockquote><br />\n0.00%"},{"pid":"d45c86abc000430e4557ff9b4aabae788321d05a","tid":2134704,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e154f6c221bc6f6292477b7a46e3b3f5097f14","tid":2134704,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"風紀Wow咗好耐-.-"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}